2019 and 2020</font><br>HB0307</pre></b></center><p>&nbsp;</p>Introduced , by Rep. David McSweeney<p>&nbsp;</p><b>SYNOPSIS AS INTRODUCED:</b><br>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td class="xsl"><code>
